</tr>
</table>
<p>Even though ऋ, ॠ, ऌ, ॡ are present in Nepal Bhasa, they are rarely used. Instead, some of the experts are suggesting to include अय्(aya)and आय्(aaya) in the list of vowels.<sup id="cite_ref-15" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-15"><span>[</span>16<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nepal_Bhasa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Consonants">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Consonants">Consonants</span></h3>
<p>The consonants, called BaAkha(बाआखः), used in Nepal Bhasa are:</p>
<table class="wikitable" align="center" width="250">
