<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nepal_Bhasa&amp;action=edit&amp;section=32" title="Edit section: Relationship">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Relationship">Relationship</span></h2>
